{"tid":1163562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來日本都會比文化入侵 BTS靜岡公演最終場 日本275座電影院辦直播","createTime":"2019-05-20T13:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T23:31:44.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0b17c047a297e879e53f1a26e356270370236d","tid":1163562,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/05/190211014602100707-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F190211014602100707-600x400.jpg&h=12ae7e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防彈少年團（BTS）出席第61屆葛萊美獎頒獎典禮資料照。 (Neilson Barnard/Getty Images for The Recording Academy)<br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2019年05月20日訊】（大紀元記者曾薇心編譯報導）韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（ BTS）的日本官方SNS今天（20日）宣布，防彈少年團7月14日在日本靜岡縣小笠山綜合運 動公園體育場舉辦的「BTS WORLD TOUR &lsquo;LOVE YOURSELF: SPEAK YOURSELF&rsquo;」演唱會， <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將在日本全國共275座電影院同時直播。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團的世界巡迴演唱會日本站，預計於7月6日及7日在可容納超過4萬人的日本大阪 長居陸上競技場（洋馬長居體育場）開唱。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他們還將在7月13日及14日於可容納超過5萬人 的靜岡縣小笠山綜合運動公園體育場開唱，而本次將於日本全國275座電影院轉播的是本 次巡演的最終場，別具意義。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ndoublehds: 都抽不到票落選六次（恨XDD<br />\nshirooo: 一樓你不孤單QQ<br />\narisucho: 完全抽不到票...<br />\nandiiiknow: 落選+1......好想去日本看演唱會QQ<br />\njmclpig9: 日巡落選加上見面會落選 到現在還在灰心QQ<br />\nStaciayeon: 落選+1 QQ"},{"pid":"ecefc142076a6004077d5c6f575732f3b1153198","tid":1163562,"uid":213300,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"感覺到牙邊股氣嚟緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49523712215e7baa16f855c7157a31b69050adc5","tid":1163562,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecefc142076a6004077d5c6f575732f3b1153198","tid":1163562,"uid":213300,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"